@Node InterTalk

 INTERTALK 2.0

     Tap into a whole new world with this versatile comms program.

     InterTalk 2.0 lets you communicate with an international network
of computers and bulletin boards.  The program's new Workbench 2
styling is a pleasure to use, even on older 1.2/1.3 Amigas.  Exchange
data and information with other computers and bulletin boards.
Generate attractive printouts with Interactivision's brand new, user-
friendly print manager.  InterTalk 2.0 is extremely easy to use,
thanks to its informative and concisely written manual, which has been
designed to help you master the program as quickly as possible.

     Although telecommunications is a complicated top, InterTalk 2.0
makes it breathtakingly simple, by supporting virtually all known
modems.  Its Fast menu lets you configure the program to suit YOUR
modem, so you can whiz your data back and forth at speeds up to a
stunning 115,200 baud.  InterTalk 2.0 recognises both ANSI and TTY
terminals, using ASCII, X, Y and Z modem protocols, with both 16 and
32 bit CRC.  Of course, you don't need to worry about any of that;
just load InterTalk 2.0 and phone your favourite bulletin boards and
databases ....

     And for those who thought that bulletin boards were boring; think
again!  Because InterTalk 2.0 supports the industry standard for
graphics (ANSI), your communications can be brought to life with
vibrant colours and eye-catching graphics.  Naturally, InterTalk 2.0
makes extensive use of the Amiga's Intuition interface, with pull-down
menus and windows.  Furthermore, the program's most frequently used
functions are instantly available via a set of on-screen icons.  Disk
operations such as Rename and Delete can also be accessed at the mere
click of a button.

     InterTalk 2.0 is just one of a suite of programs, therefore you
can use other programs in the Interrange to edit the data that you
download.  Read the enclosed literature for further information about
the entire Interactivision range.

     @{" Continue " link InterSpread}

@Endnode

@Node InterSpread

 INTERSPREAD 2.0

     The perfect solution for sophisticated numerical analysis and
calculations

     InterSpread 2.0 puts you firmly in the driving seat when it comes
to forecasting, budgeting, cash-flow analysis and much, much more.
The program's Workbench 2 styling is a pleasure to use, even on older
1.2/1.3 Amigas.  Take advantage of the built-in graph functions to
present your data in an easy-to-understand format.  Generate
attractive print-outs with Interactivision's brand new, user-friendly
print manager.  InterSpread 2.0 is extremely easy to use, thanks to
its informative and concisely written manual, which has been designed
to help you master the program as quickly as possible.

     InterSpread 2.0 includes an extensive library of financial,
mathematical, statistical, trigonomic and conditional functions, which
can be applied to data in any of up to 10,508,949 cells.  Yes, you
read that correctly, InterSpread 2.0 can support more than ten MILLION
cells at once.  For really tough problems, just put your feet up and
relax while InterSpread 2.0's point-and-click macros take over the
brain-work for you.

     When it comes to presentation, InterSpread 2.0 has equally
impressive credentials.  Data can be represented graphically, using
one of eight different types of graph.  These can be output with equal
clarity on colour on monochrome printers.  Naturally, InterSpread 2.0
makes extensive use of the Amiga's Intuition interface, with pull-down
menus and windows.  Furthermore, the program's most frequently used
functions are instantly available via a set of on-screen icons.  Disk
operations such as Rename and Delete can also be accessed at the mere
click of a button.

     InterSpread 2.0 is just one of a suite of Inter-applications,
therefore it can send data directly to InterWord 2.0 for immediate
inclusion in your documents.  Read the enclosed literature for further
information about the entire Interactivision range.

     @{" Continue " link "InterBase"}

@Endnode

@Node InterBase

INTERBASE 2.0

     The ultimate data storage solution.

     InterBase 2.0 retains all the power of its predecessor, presented
via a greatly enhanced user interface.   The program's Workbench 2
styling is a pleasure to use, even on old 1.2/1.3 Amigas.  Create and
manipulate databases limited in size only by the capacity of your
storage medium (floppy disk, hard drive, etc.).  You'll be amazed at
the power and versatility of dynamic strings (a uniquely implemented
concept).  Generate attractive print-outs with Interactivision's brand
new, user-friendly print manager.  InterBase 2.0 is extremely easy to
use thanks to its informative and concisely written manual, which has
been designed to help you master the program as quickly as possible.

     The program's graphic interface quickly allows you to understand
the concepts of a relational database.  Defining your database is
simplicity itself thanks to the flexibility of the program's dynamic
strings which give you fields of virtually unlimited size.
Relationships between databases can be easily defined for economical
use of both your storage space and time.  Furthermore, the InterBase
2.0 screen-layout functions give you unsurpassed flexibility when
designing the way that your data should be presented, both on-screen,
and in the final printed copy.

     InterBase 2.0 offers you maximum flexibility when defining the
priority and criteria used for sorting your records.  IFF-ILBM screens
can be displayed simply by clicking on user-defined buttons.
Naturally, InterBase 2.0 makes extensive use of the Amiga's Intuition
surface, with pull-down menus and windows. Furthermore, the program's
most frequently used functions are instantly available via a set of
on-screen icons.  Disk operations such as Rename and Delete can also
be accessed at the mere click of a button.

     InterBase 2.0 is just one of a suite of Inter-applications,
therefore it can send data directly to InterWord 2.0 for immediate
inclusion in your documents via the mail-merge function.  Read the
enclosed literature for further information about the entire
Interactivision range.

     @{" Continue " link "InterOffice"}

@Endnode

@Node InterOffice

INTEROFFICE 2.0

INTERWORD 2.0

     InterWord 2.0 is easy to use, and its standardised interface even
lets you exchange data with the other InterOffice 2.0 applications.
Data can be imported from InterBase 2.0 using the mail-merge option
and statistics can be transferred from InterSpread 2.0.

     InterWord 2.0 includes a unique, multi-level spelling checker
with a massive 110,000 word dictionary.  Its comprehensive file
management options such as Delete, Rename and MakeDir let you organise
your disks without having to exist from the program.  Better yet, its
indexing facility will automatically generate cross-referenced indices
for inclusion in your documents.

     Of course, InterWord 2.0 includes all of the standard word
processor functions such as Search and Replace, headers and footers,
timed auto back-ups and hyphenation.  These are supported by
invaluable options which will give you precise statistics about a
document, including its Legibility Index (LIX).

INTERSPREAD 2.0

     InterSpread 2.0 puts you firmly in the driving seat when it comes
to forecasting, budgeting, cash-flow analysis and much, much more.
The program includes an extensive library of financial, mathematical,
statistical, trigonometric and conditional functions which can be
applied to data in any of up to 10,508,949 cells.  Yes, you read that
correctly, InterSpread 2.0 can support over ten MILLION cells at once!
For really tough problems, just put your feet up and relax while
InterSpread 2.0's point-and-click macros take over the brain-work for
you.

     When it comes to presentation, InterSpread 2.0 has equally
impressive credentials.  Data can be represented graphically using one
of eight different types of graph, and these can be output with equal
clarity or monochrome printers.

INTERBASE 2.0

     InterOffice 2.0 is the only integrated software package to
include database.  The InterBase 2.0 graphical interface helps you to
understand the concepts of a relational database, and its layout
functions give you unsurpassed flexibility when designing the way that
your data will be presented, both on screen and in the final printed
copy.  This versatility even extends to encompass the format of your
files on disk, ensuring maximum compatibility with additional
applications that you may be using.

     InterBase 2.0 also features a unique type of dynamic string which
gives you fields of virtually unlimited size.  You can even store IFF
picture files at the click of a button.

     Databases created with InterBase 2.0 are limited in size only by
the capacity of your storage medium (floppy disk, hard drive, etc).
These may be password protected and multiple levels of security can be
defined allowing variable access to users of the same database.


INTERTALK 2.0

     InterTalk 2.0 lets you communicate with an international network
of computers and bulletin boards.  The program's Workbench 2 styling
